{"tid":1092352,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"比交通警推","createTime":"2019-04-04T18:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T08:42:14.000Z","uid":58503,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"066eb01e7cfe6f5b914d8783dd7c1c35bdea7b38","tid":1092352,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"頭先返屋企嗰陣，係堅拿道天橋有架電單車行我後面。到我落告士打道嗰陣，佢就開始推我。咁我睇一睇速度，自己開緊40，我以為自己開得太慢，所以就比油希望拉開個距離，點知佢照比油追。我係慢線加速到115都拉唔開個距離，我就決定唔再比油減速。係我臨轉入駱克道，架電單車去左隔離線爬我頭。我原本重諗係咩野人咁仆街，竟然係交通警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰一刻佢望住我，我又望住佢。兩秒後大家就分道揚鑣。"},{"pid":"e3487671772a850165e31b6763f7faeefc5c407a","tid":1092352,"uid":79410,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T18:57:35.000Z","msg":"40俾人推到115? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知D 老隱就係咁捉人超速."},{"pid":"989496d4d9104cb3faecfe9a7c7e4a4e3ffe5bf9","tid":1092352,"uid":195714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"重dup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783c60d5391ef3e9431cf8c1b87ba993d1f7f825","tid":1092352,"uid":60412,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"比人推就渣快d on99"},{"pid":"0fff2050b081f99049f48cd58c104ba5ed585528","tid":1092352,"uid":56338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"正路你係慢線唔會推你"},{"pid":"6b4c5418c8ebfd700ac9e0cd99640f2b369f8dac","tid":1092352,"uid":68896,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"其實你合法車速行車，佢又唔閃燈，跟本唔駛理佢"},{"pid":"9167b514746e5c0b9a04996a2f12c89297ae1e6e","tid":1092352,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:23:39.000Z","msg":"掉咗個放大鏡佢啦，人地有排都未埋到嚟呀<br />\n一係有無＋－波呀，下次一嘢拉嚟一波"},{"pid":"74a252ae502126a26c08ae0e89e370266db9f92f","tid":1092352,"uid":139413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"reply